data.comment: The whistle has gone to start the match.
Mjallby awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 2, Per Martin Melin awards the away team a throw-in.
Djurgarden are coming forward and Emir Kujovic gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
Ball goes out of play for a Mjallby goal kick.
In the minute 3, Throw-in for Mjallby at Tele2 Arena.
In Stockholm, Djurgarden push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
Throw-in Djurgarden.
In the minute 6, Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
Mjallby to take a throw-in in Djurgarden territory.
In the minute 8, Free kick Mjallby.
Per Martin Melin signals a free kick to Mjallby in their own half.
In Stockholm Mjallby attack through Besard Sabovic. The finish is off target, however.
In the minute 12, Per Martin Melin awards Djurgarden a goal kick.
Emir Kujovic of Djurgarden is pulled up for offside.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
In the minute 14, Djurgarden have a goal kick.
Mjallby needs to be cautious. Djurgarden have an attacking throw-in.
Throw-in high up the field for Djurgarden in Stockholm.
In the minute 15, Ball safe as Mjallby is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Throw-in for Mjallby at Tele2 Arena.
Emmanuel Banda for Djurgarden drives towards goal at Tele2 Arena. But the finish is unsuccessful.
In the minute 18, Goal kick for Mjallby at Tele2 Arena.
Djurgarden's Emir Kujovic attacks the ball with his head but his effort fails to hit the target.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Stockholm.
In the minute 19, Throw-in for Mjallby in the half of Djurgarden.
Can Mjallby get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Djurgarden's half?
Throw-in for Djurgarden in their own half.
In the minute 22, Djurgarden have a dangerous throw-in.
Per Martin Melin signals a Djurgarden throw-in in Mjallby's half.
Mjallby have a goal kick.
In the minute 25, Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Per Martin Melin awards the away team a throw-in.
In Stockholm a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 29, Moses Ogbu scores to make it 0-1 at Tele2 Arena.
David Lofquist with an assist there.
Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
In the minute 31, Fredrik Ulvestad is booked for the home team.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Stockholm.
Per Martin Melin signals a free kick to Djurgarden in their own half.
In the minute 34, Ball goes out of play for a Mjallby goal kick.
Ball safe as Djurgarden is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Djurgarden's Emir Kujovic has run offside.
In the minute 36, Mjallby awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Djurgarden awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 38, Jesper Karlstrom for Djurgarden has been booked by Per Martin Melin and receives a first yellow card.
Free kick for Djurgarden in the half of Mjallby.
Per Martin Melin signals a free kick to Mjallby in their own half.
In the minute 44, Mjallby's Mamudo Moro misses with an attempt on goal.
Goal kick for Djurgarden at Tele2 Arena.
The ref's whistle signals the end of the first-half.
In the minute 46, The second-half is underway in Stockholm.
Djurgarden make their first substitution with Curtis Edwards replacing Kevin Walker.
Jonathan Ring is replacing Kalle Holmberg for the home team.
In the minute 47, Throw-in for Djurgarden in the half of Mjallby.
Djurgarden to take a throw-in in Mjallby territory.
Djurgarden drive upfield and Curtis Edwards gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Mjallby defender.
In the minute 50, Per Martin Melin signals a free kick to Djurgarden.
Goal! The home team draw level at 1-1 through a header from Emir Kujovic.
Great play from Emmanuel Banda to set up the goal.
In the minute 52, Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
Mjallby's Jesper Lofgren gets in a shot on goal at Tele2 Arena. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Mjallby's Mamudo Moro gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 53, Per Martin Melin awards Djurgarden a goal kick.
Throw-in Mjallby.
Djurgarden's Emir Kujovic breaks free at Tele2 Arena. But the strike goes wide of the post.
In the minute 54, Per Martin Melin awards Mjallby a goal kick.
In Stockholm a free kick has been awarded the away team.
Agony for Mjallby as Jesper Lofgren 's header comes back off the post and is cleared.
In the minute 59, Jonathan Ring for Djurgarden gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Goal kick for Mjallby at Tele2 Arena.
Per Martin Melin blows against Djurgarden's Emir Kujovic for offside.
In the minute 60, Per Martin Melin signals a free kick to Djurgarden.
Per Martin Melin signals a free kick to Mjallby in their own half.
Per Martin Melin signals a Mjallby throw-in in Djurgarden's half.
In the minute 62, Important block from the Mjallby defence as Curtis Edwards fires in a strike for Djurgarden.
Djurgarden have been awarded a corner by Per Martin Melin.
Corner awarded to Djurgarden.
In the minute 64, Djurgarden move into a 2-1 lead through a Jonathan Augustinsson header.
Aslak Witry instrumental with a fine assist.
Mamudo Moro for Mjallby is whistled offside.
In the minute 67, Mjallby's David Batanero gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Djurgarden defender.
Free kick Djurgarden.
Mjallby have a goal kick.
In the minute 68, Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Ball goes out of play for a Mjallby goal kick.
Mamudo Moro (Mjallby) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 78, Free kick for Mjallby in the half of Djurgarden.
At Tele2 Arena, Erik Berg for the home team has been yellow-carded. He will miss the next match due to a suspension!
Thomas Lagerlof is making the team's third substitution at Tele2 Arena with Elliot Kack replacing Emmanuel Banda.
In the minute 79, Joel Nilsson is on a sub for Jonathan Tamimi for Mjallby.
The away team have replaced Mamudo Moro with Jacob Bergstrom. This is the second substitution made today by Marcus Lantz.
In the minute 80, Mjallby have been awarded a corner by Per Martin Melin.
The away team replace David Batanero with Taylor Silverholt.
Free kick for Djurgarden in their own half.
Per Martin Melin awards the away team a throw-in.
In the minute 81, Thomas Lagerlof (Djurgarden) is making a fourth substitution, with Jesper Nyholm replacing Emir Kujovic.
Corner awarded to Mjallby.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Stockholm.
In the minute 86, Mjallby are whistled for offside.
Throw-in for Mjallby at Tele2 Arena.
Djurgarden are too eager and fall into an offside trap.
In the minute 87, Djurgarden drive forward but Elliot Kack is judged offside.
David Lofquist (Mjallby) gets a yellow card.
In Stockholm a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 89, Jacob Une Larsson (Djurgarden) gets booked by Per Martin Melin, and will miss the next match due to the number of yellow cards received this season.
Mjallby have been awarded a corner by Per Martin Melin.
Free kick Mjallby.
In Stockholm Mjallby drive forward through Besard Sabovic. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Mjallby push forward at Tele2 Arena and Eric Bjorkander gets in a great header. The attempt is cleared by the Djurgarden defence.
Ball safe as Mjallby is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Per Martin Melin will wait an extra 3 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 2nd half.
Can Djurgarden capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Mjallby's half?
Per Martin Melin signals a throw-in for Djurgarden, close to Mjallby's area.
Throw-in Mjallby.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
Free kick for Djurgarden in their own half.
Per Martin Melin blows to end the match. The final score is 2-1.
